  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  head and neck cancer patients (localized to the larynx, pharynx and oral cavity)
             treated with curative radiotherapy

          -  complete loss of tumor

          -  WHO performance status between 0-1 and expected ability to complete the training
             protocol

          -  No parenteral feeding

          -  above the age of 18

          -  written concent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  other malignant diseases

          -  pregnancy

          -  undergoing systematic resistance training or creatin ingestion

          -  Alcohol abuse
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
